channel.title: Help! how to change default gateway
channel.description: hey everyone i have made my server but it is only me that can connect beacuse of my default gate way it changes when i restart my computer i think. i am using talk talk broadband internet dont worry bout the talk talk its something for the phone. i have been on guides and i have been on start>run>cmd and my default gateway changes whenn i reconnect to internet or restart computer. but can some 1 seriously help me?!? iv spent like 3 hours trying to change my gateway to the default and also please tell me how to get my server up n runing after that. . make your intructions easy to understand coz im not very good with computers and tell me what to type. ThAnKs. i think this should help alot of people . :cool:
